            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>特許通訊(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:CHTR:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/CHTR\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">CHTR-US</a>)截至台北時間25日21:30股價下跌49.49美元，報330.51美元，跌幅13.02%，成交量318,621（股），盤中最高價330.51美元、最低價329.00美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：+0.17%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：+0.14%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：+0.18%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：+0.12%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>特許通訊(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:CHTR:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/CHTR\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">CHTR-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：-0.93%</li> <li>近 1 月：-5.82%</li> <li>近 3 月：+13.32%</li> <li>近 6 月：+3.38%</li> <li>今年以來：+10.86%</li></ul></section></main>",
